author: philip
msg: Make the 1.6 compatibility code set the copied field of svn_wc_entry_t
to TRUE for deletes within a copy as that is the behaviour of 1.6.  This
interface is no longer used by WCNG code, it is only used by clients that
want 1.6 style information, so it should match 1.6 where possible.
(read_one_entry): Set copied=TRUE for delete within a copy.
(deletion_details): Expect delete within a copy to be copied='+'.
(delete_in_copy_upgrade): Expect delete within a copy to be copied='+',
(relocate_deleted_missing_copied): Expect delete within a copy to be
copy_delete_undo): Expect delete within a copy to be copied='+'.
